<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Welcome to {{organizationName}}</title>
</head>

<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background:#f3f4f6;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;">

<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
<tr>
<td align="center">

<!-- Card -->
<table width="620" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"
style="background:#ffffff;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;border:1px solid #e5e7eb;box-shadow:0 10px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.06)">

<!-- Header -->
<tr>
<td style="padding:26px 32px;background:#16A34A;color:#ffffff;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.4px">
{{organizationName}}
</td>
</tr>

<!-- Greeting -->
<tr>
<td style="padding:32px 32px 10px 32px;font-size:15px;color:#374151;line-height:24px">

<p style="margin-top:0;font-size:16px">
Hello <strong>{{firstName}} {{lastName}}</strong>,
</p>

<p>
🎉 Welcome aboard! Your organization <strong>{{organizationName}}</strong> has been successfully created.
</p>

<p>
You're now all set to start managing your workspace, team members, and accounts seamlessly.
</p>

</td>
</tr>

<!-- Info Box -->
<tr>
<td style="padding:0 32px 25px 32px">

<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"
style="background:#f0fdf4;border-radius:10px;border:1px solid #bbf7d0">

<tr>
<td colspan="2"
style="padding:14px 18px;font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#065f46;border-bottom:1px solid #bbf7d0">
Account Details
</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td style="padding:12px 18px;font-size:13px;color:#065f46;width:160px">Organization</td>
<td style="padding:12px 18px;font-size:14px;color:#064e3b">{{organizationName}}</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td style="padding:12px 18px;font-size:13px;color:#065f46">Email</td>
<td style="padding:12px 18px;font-size:14px;color:#064e3b">{{email}}</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td style="padding:12px 18px;font-size:13px;color:#065f46">Role</td>
<td style="padding:12px 18px;font-size:14px;color:#064e3b">Owner</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td style="padding:12px 18px;font-size:13px;color:#065f46">Created At</td>
<td style="padding:12px 18px;font-size:14px;color:#064e3b">{{createdAt}}</td>
</tr>

</table>

</td>
</tr>

<!-- CTA -->
<tr>
<td style="padding:0 32px 32px 32px;text-align:center">

<a href="{{dashboardUrl}}"
style="display:inline-block;background:#16A34A;color:#ffffff;padding:14px 26px;border-radius:8px;text-decoration:none;font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;box-shadow:0 6px 18px rgba(22,163,74,0.3)">
Go to Dashboard
</a>

</td>
</tr>

<!-- Message -->
<tr>
<td style="padding:0 32px 25px 32px;font-size:15px;color:#374151;line-height:24px">

<p>
You can now:
</p>

<ul style="padding-left:18px;margin-top:8px">
<li>Create and manage accounts</li>
<li>Invite team members</li>
<li>Assign roles and permissions</li>
<li>Track your organization activity</li>
</ul>

<p style="margin-top:16px">
If you have any questions or need assistance, our team is here to help.
</p>

</td>
</tr>

<!-- Support -->
<tr>
<td style="padding:22px 32px;background:#f9fafb;border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb">

<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
<tr>

<td style="font-size:14px;color:#374151">
Need help?
</td>

<td align="right">
<a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}"
style="background:#16A34A;color:#ffffff;padding:10px 16px;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px">
Contact Support
</a>
</td>

</tr>
</table>

<p style="margin-top:10px;font-size:13px;color:#6b7280">
{{supportEmail}}
</p>

</td>
</tr>

<!-- Footer -->
<tr>
<td style="padding:28px 32px;background:#f3f4f6;font-size:13px;color:#6b7280">

<p style="margin:0 0 8px 0">
Best Regards,<br>
<strong>{{organizationName}} Team</strong>
</p>

<p style="margin:8px 0 0 0">
© {{year}} {{organizationName}}. All rights reserved.
</p>

<p style="margin-top:14px;font-size:12px;color:#9ca3af">
This email confirms your successful onboarding and organization setup.
</p>

</td>
</tr>

</table>

</td>
</tr>
</table>

</body>
</html>